    "description": "DM Solutions Co.,Ltd engages in the marketing business in Japan. It operates in three segments: Direct Mail Business, Internet Business, and Apparel Business. The company offers logistics solutions, including support services for shipping and mail-order operations, such as ordering processing, payment services, and customer service; and direct mail marketing services comprising direct mail and mail delivery services; machinery and equipment, which include film wrapping machine, bus crow printing machine, film envelope inserter, and paper envelope inserter; security system; printing services, such as pamphlets, booklets, public relations materials, direct mail, envelopes, advertising flyers, business cards, postcards, invitations, posters, printing slips and forms, calendars and fans, and tack stickers; and sellmarketing. It also provides web marketing services comprising SEO consulting, content marketing, website creation, advertising management, shopify production agency, and web customer acquisition support tool intimateSEOl; media production and management; operating media; and design management, including planning and design, as well as production, such as corporate websites, web advertisement, paper media, video production, assistance with exhibition participation, logo creation, and store tool design. In addition, the company operates BeeMe, a Manuka honey specialty store; pureLi, a lifestyle brand; and RHET, a D2C car care brand. Further, it sells clothing and other products through e-commerce sites. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Musashino, Japan."
